title: Hidden Desktop v1.2
description:
Hidden.Desktop v1.2 | 1.65MB

Everything you do on your PC with Hidden Desktop is completely and securely hidden with no visible traces
Perfect for PCs that are shared with others, Laptops that have sensitive information (which may be stolen), and for those who require extreme privacy from hackers, or intruders of any kind. Hidden Desktop creates a new private, hidden desktop where you can install your favorite apps, create and save documents, pictures, and browse the internet. All files, data and activity is completely hidden and secure nobody will know it exists, nor will they be able to access it. Hidden Desktop allows any user to create a safe haven to work from where browsing history, cookies, pictures, documents or files will never be found
